<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="ko">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <title>Lines — Station8</title>
    <link rel="icon" type="image/svg+xml" href="/favicon.svg">
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="/css/design.css">
</head>
<body>
{{> _nav }}

<div class="swe-container" style="padding-top: var(--space-xxl); padding-bottom: var(--space-section);">

    <div class="swe-flex-between swe-mb-xl">
        <div>
            <h1 class="swe-display-lg" style="margin: 0;">Lines</h1>
            <p class="swe-body-md swe-mute" style="margin: var(--space-sm) 0 0;">활성 라인 정의 ({{totalCount}}건) — 노선도로 보거나 빌더에서 새 라인을 만든다</p>
        </div>
        <a href="/line/builder" class="swe-btn-primary">+ New Line</a>
    </div>

    <!-- #142 — 검색 / 태그 필터 -->
    <div class="swe-card-elevated swe-mb-xl">
        <form method="get" action="/line/definitions" class="swe-grid swe-grid-3" style="gap: var(--space-md); align-items: end;">
            <div>
                <label for="defs-name">Line name</label>
                <input type="text" id="defs-name" name="name" class="swe-input"
                       value="{{#filterName}}{{filterName}}{{/filterName}}" placeholder="이름 부분일치">
            </div>
            <div>
                <label for="defs-tag">Tag</label>
                <input type="text" id="defs-tag" name="tag" class="swe-input"
                       value="{{#filterTag}}{{filterTag}}{{/filterTag}}" placeholder="정확 일치 (e.g. etl)">
            </div>
            <div style="display:flex; gap: var(--space-md); justify-content: flex-end;">
                <a href="/line/definitions" class="swe-btn-secondary">Reset</a>
                <button type="submit" class="swe-btn-primary">Apply</button>
            </div>
        </form>
        {{#hasTagCloud}}
        <div style="margin-top: var(--space-md); display: flex; flex-wrap: wrap; gap: var(--space-xs);">
            <span class="swe-mute" style="font-size: 12px; align-self: center; margin-right: var(--space-xs);">Tag cloud:</span>
            {{#tagCloud}}
            <a href="/line/definitions?tag={{tag}}"
               class="swe-tag swe-tag-{{colorClass}}"
               title="{{count}} 개 라인"
               style="text-decoration: none;">
                {{tag}} <span class="swe-mute" style="font-size: 10px;">{{count}}</span>
            </a>
            {{/tagCloud}}
        </div>
        {{/hasTagCloud}}
    </div>

    <div class="swe-card" style="padding: 0;">
        <table class="swe-table">
            <thead>
            <tr>
                <th>Line Name</th>
                <th>Tags</th>
                <th>Description</th>
                <th>Version</th>
                <th>Created</th>
                <th class="swe-text-right">Action</th>
            </tr>
            </thead>
            <tbody>
            {{#definitions}}
            <tr>
                <td><strong>{{definitionNm}}</strong></td>
                <td>
                    {{#tagViews}}
                    <a href="/line/definitions?tag={{tag}}" class="swe-tag swe-tag-{{colorClass}}" style="text-decoration:none; margin-right: 4px;">{{tag}}</a>
                    {{/tagViews}}
                </td>
                <td class="swe-mute">{{#description}}{{description}}{{/description}}{{^description}}—{{/description}}</td>
                <td>v{{versionNo}}</td>
                <td class="swe-mute">{{#regDt}}{{regDt}}{{/regDt}}{{^regDt}}—{{/regDt}}</td>
                <td class="swe-text-right">
                    <a href="/line/definitions/{{id}}" class="swe-btn-tertiary swe-btn-sm">Preview</a>
                    <a href="/line/builder?id={{id}}" class="swe-btn-tertiary swe-btn-sm">Edit</a>
                </td>
            </tr>
            {{/definitions}}
            {{^definitions}}
            <tr>
                <td colspan="6" style="text-align: center; padding: var(--space-section) 0; color: var(--mute);">
                    {{#filterTag}}태그 "{{filterTag}}" 일치 없음{{/filterTag}}{{^filterTag}}{{#filterName}}이름 "{{filterName}}" 일치 없음{{/filterName}}{{^filterName}}아직 라인이 없습니다. <a href="/line/builder" class="swe-ink">Builder</a>에서 새 라인을 만들어보세요.{{/filterName}}{{/filterTag}}
                </td>
            </tr>
            {{/definitions}}
            </tbody>
        </table>
        {{> _pagination }}
    </div>

</div>
</body>
</html>
